source.name: The Pentagon Channel - Exchange on Air video feed
source.description: EXchange On Air invites Pentagon Channel viewers into the world of the Army and Air Force Exchange Service. Fun, relevant and informative, this monthly video program tackles issues that face our armed service members and families everyday.
